# Meeting Summarizer
Objective: Transcribe meeting audio and generate action-oriented summaries.

## Features
- Upload audio, get transcript
- Summaries: short summary, decisions, action items
- Pluggable ASR adapters (OpenAI, Azure, Google)
- Simple frontend to upload files

## Setup
1. Clone repo
2. Create virtualenv
3. Set env vars (OPENAI_API_KEY etc.)
4. Run uvicorn backend.app:app --reload

